#: ../../language/error_codes/E0063.md:1
msgid "E0063"
msgstr "E0063"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0063.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `syntax_lint`"
msgstr "警告名称：`syntax_lint`"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0063.md:5
msgid "Syntax lint warning."
msgstr "语法 lint 警告。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0063.md:7
msgid ""
"This warning category is used for valid code patterns that the compiler "
"accepts but discourages through syntax lint diagnostics."
msgstr "此警告类别用于编译器接受但通过语法 lint 诊断不推荐的合法代码模式。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0063.md:10
msgid ""
"No checked example is currently included for this warning. Add an "
"`0063_error` fixture only when there is a compact stable-toolchain "
"snippet that reproduces `Warning: [0063]`."
msgstr ""
"此警告目前没有包含已检查的示例。只有在存在能够复现 `Warning: [0063]` "
"的简短稳定工具链代码片段时，才添加 `0063_error` fixture。"
